Get an adrenaline rush racing on the tracks where Ducati made history! Hit the gas on 5 faithfully-reproduced country tracks and 8 official circuits, including the Ducati fansâ€™ favourite, the Misano World Circuit - Marco Simoncelli, reliving the exploits of those who made history.
